    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a medium sized pot over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1694436579324-x200.jpg",
