            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the bacon is golden, add the <strong>sliced leek</strong> and <strong>diced carrot</strong> to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> with 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[1.1L]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.4L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1694436585429-x200.jpg",
