          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1694436588755-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>creamy stock </strong>with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 8-10 min or until the vegetables are tender and the stock has thickened slightly – this is your <strong>southern-style butter bean & bacon soup</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1694436591296-x200.jpg",
