          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1694436594082-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>southern-style butter bean & bacon soup </strong>in bowls and top with the <strong>crispy kale</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>garlic toasts </strong>to the side and sprinkle the kale with the <strong>remaining southern fried seasoning</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
